How beautiful is football? - Shakira films joyous mood after Barcelona winner 
9-3-2017 
It should be no surprise that songstress Shakira was among the most vocal Barcelona supporters in the Camp Nou on Wednesday.

Un momento para los anales de la historia!!! Shak pic.twitter.com/I4HSJeKLCm — Shakira (@shakira) March 8, 2017

Shakira, whose partner is Barcelona centre-back Gerard Pique, was in attendance as the Catalans pulled off the greatest comeback in Champions League history against Paris Saint-Germain to progress to the last eight.

Qué momento!!! Y qué bonito es el fútbol!!! pic.twitter.com/GOkWyEjUdS — Shakira (@shakira) March 8, 2017

Barcelona overturned a 4-0 first-leg deficit with a thrilling 6-1 win, Sergi Roberto’s last-gasp goal sealing their progression.

🌍📰 La prensa mundial se rinde a la hazaña del Barça https://t.co/Ik03eIQ9q9 #ForçaBarça pic.twitter.com/MDZ3IvvilI — FC Barcelona (@FCBarcelona_es) March 9, 2017

